headline.print_headline: Peugeot Signs Dongfeng Deal, Recovery Hurdles Remain
headline.main: Peugeot Signs Dongfeng Deal, Recovery Hurdles Remain

lead_paragraph: PSA Peugeot Citroen's tie-up with China's Dongfeng was signed on Wednesday, bringing the French carmaker much-needed cash and greater access to Asia but leaving major challenges ahead.
